These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, lily
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, thriller
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, surfing
There 3 different types of food: garlic, grapes, peas
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating grapes is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person watching thriller movies##2
5. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person who growsdaffodil##6
6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growslily##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3     |
| Flower         | lily | bellflower | daffodil  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | disaster     | thriller |
| Sport         | cycling     | basketball   | surfing  |
| Food     | garlic        | grapes   | peas      |

