.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-3::.
House: victorian, cottage, modern
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, japanese, italian
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, paramedic, teacher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, family, mystery
1. the japanese is the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
3. the italian is on the left of the teacher##1
4. the teacher is not the italian##6
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the manager##1
6. the modern house is between the italian and the cottage house##2
7. the modern house is somewhere between the manager and the japanese##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |
| House      | victorian           | modern  | cottage |
| Nationality         | italian | thai   | japanese  |
| Job           | manager       | teacher   | paramedic   |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | adventure | mystery     |

