.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, water
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, airplane
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, gospel, metal
There 3 different types of food: tomato, banana, papaya
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person driving the scooter is the fan of classical##1
4. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person eating banana is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person driving the airplane##7
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
8. the person eating banana is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | water       | juice     | milk         |
| Transport         | airplane | scooter    | taxi      |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | classical | gospel       |
| Food         | papaya  | banana    | tomato |

