.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-5::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, ferret
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, pop, salsa
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the rabbit##7
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the fan of salsa is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3     |
| Pet          | goat | ferret   | rabbit  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | classical    | pop      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | 7up     | fanta |
| Sport         | skiing   | snowboarding | surfing  |

