The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose, daisy
City: london, paris, colone
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, soccer, tennis
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
4. the person traveling to colone is not the project-manager##6
5. the person who growssunflower is somewhere between the coach and the person who growsdaisy##7
6. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
7. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |    3     |
