3. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
4. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person eating orange and the fan of trance##7
7. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the tower house##3
8. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| House      | craftsman     | tower | wooden |
| Food          | cranberry | cauliflower   | orange      |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | techno        | disco       |
| Sport   | cricket  | swimming      | rugby     |

