3. the person playing domino is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
6. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the american##7
7. the italian is in the middle##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |
