4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person who's hobby is cooking##7

.:: Answer ::.
