3. the pilot is somewhere between the designer and the person eating lime##7
4. the person eating kiwi is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person eating lime##7
5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating corn##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the entrepreneur and the person who growsorchid##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |      3       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | soy-milk      | coffee       |
| Job        | designer | pilot         | entrepreneur |
| Food        | corn     | kiwi        | lime         |
| Flower      | orchid  | aconite | azalea      |

 